Regular k-point mesh          ! Type of k-point grid
0                              ! 0 -> determine number of k points automatically
Gamma-centered                     ! generate a Gamma-centered mesh
1  1  1         ! subdivisions N_1, N_2 and N_3 along the reciprocal lattice vectors
0  0  0                         ! optional shift of the mesh (s_1, s_2, s_3)
